# 🚢 XGB CO₂ & Fuel-Consumption Predictor

This Streamlit-based web application predicts **fuel consumption (FC)** and **CO₂ emissions** for various ship technical scenarios using an XGBoost regression model, enhanced by Monte Carlo simulations.

---

## 🔐 Login

Access is **restricted** to authorized users.  
Please contact **Hamid** (project creator) to request login credentials.

---

## 📦 Features

- Interactive input for ship parameters
- ML-powered predictions (XGBoost)
- Visual comparison across 5 retrofit scenarios
- Downloadable prediction reports (Word format)
- Password protection using `.streamlit/secrets.toml`

